1. Ovo je *zanimljiv* film. (This is an *interesting* movie.)
2. On je *zanimljiv* sagovornik. (He is an *interesting* interlocutor.)
3. Sinoć smo imali *zanimljiv* razgovor. (We had an *interesting* conversation last night.)
4. Moram pronaći nešto *zanimljivo* da pročitam. (I need to find something *interesting* to read.)
5. Ova knjiga je vrlo *zanimljiva*. (This book is very *interesting*.)
6. Nudimo vam *zanimljive* aktivnosti tokom vikenda. (We offer you *interesting* activities during the weekend.)
7. Šetnja kroz šumu bila je vrlo *zanimljiva*. (The walk through the forest was very *interesting*.)
8. Nisam čuo *zanimljiviju* priču u životu. (I have never heard a more *interesting* story in my life.)
9. Ona je jedna od naj *zanimljivijih* osoba koje poznajem. (She is one of the *most interesting* people I know.)
10. On je tako *zanimljivo* predstavio svoju ideju. (He presented his idea in such an *interesting* way.)